ActAn Act to amend the law governing financial institutions and to provide for related and consequential matters
SubjectThe law governing financial institutions and to provide for related and consequential matters (Bill C-37) *** Amendment ***
PrecisOrder fixing February 19, 2009 as the day on which sections 83, 435 and 437 of AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW GOVERNING FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS AND TO PROVIDE FOR RELATED AND CONSEQUENTIAL MATTERS. Those provisions amend the Bank Act and the Financial Consumer Agency of Canada Act.
